\n<p><strong>或技术费用。</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 请顾客保留升级时维修站开具的安装维修单，作为今后内存保修的凭证。</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 无论您是否选择升级，索尼都尊重您的选择，索尼的各级指定维修网点均可作为升级和保修的受理窗</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>口，保障您能获得备注1所述的服务。</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 对于可升级的内存容量请以维修站信息为准。</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp;您若想了解更详细的情况，敬请联系当地的索尼特约维修站或致电索尼（中国）VAIO个人电脑服务热线了解详情。&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<table align=\"left\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; height:31px\">\n			<p><strong>索尼（中国）个人电脑及平板电脑个人热线：</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; height:31px\">\n			<p><strong>400 810 2228</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; height:31px; width:152px\">&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white\">\n			<p><strong>服务时间：</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white\">\n			<p><strong>09:00 &ndash; 21:00</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; width:152px\">\n			<p><strong>(周一至周六)</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white\">\n			<p><strong>09:00 &ndash; 18:00</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; width:152px\">\n			<p><strong>(周日)</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white\">\n			<p><strong>电子邮箱：</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white\">\n			<p><strong><a href=\"mailto:vaiohelpdesk@sony.com.cn\">vaiohelpdesk@sony.com.cn</a></strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:white; width:152px\">&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs